# Nuke Console Bot

## Description
A console-based Discord bot for testing purposes in your own server.  
Features:
- Password protected (default: `sh3d0w`)
- Console-based token & server ID input
- Clears the screen at key steps
- Deletes all channels and roles in your server (use **only on your test server**)

## Installation

### Linux / macOS
```bash
chmod +x install.sh
./install.sh
Windows
Double click install.bat or run in CMD:

bat

install.bat
Usage
bash
Kodu kopyala
python nuke_bot.py
Enter password (sh3d0w)

Enter server ID

Bot will log in and be ready to run nuke commands

Warning: Use only on your own test server. Deleting roles/channels is irreversible.




